# Task Board API — repo map

Stack: **NestJS**, **Prisma 7**, **SQLite** (`@prisma/adapter-better-sqlite3`), **JWT** auth.

## Start here

| What | Where |
|------|--------|
| Bootstrap, global `ValidationPipe` | `src/main.ts` |
| Modules, global guards | `src/app.module.ts` |
| Env loading | `src/load-env.ts`, `.env` / `.env.example` |

## HTTP routes → files

| Area | Controller | Business logic |
|------|------------|----------------|
| Auth (`/auth/*`) | `src/auth/auth.controller.ts` | `src/auth/auth.service.ts` |
| Tasks (`/tasks/*`) | `src/tasks/tasks.controller.ts` | `src/tasks/tasks.service.ts` (large) |
| Users (`/users`) | `src/users/users.controller.ts` | `src/users/users.service.ts` |
| Blocks (`/blocks/*`) | `src/blocks/blocks.controller.ts` | `src/blocks/blocks.service.ts` |
| Admin (`/admin/*`) | `src/admin/admin.controller.ts` | `src/admin/admin.service.ts` |

Public routes: `@Public()` on `auth` register/login. Everything else JWT unless marked public.

## Cross-cutting (`src/common/`)

- **Guards:** `jwt-auth.guard.ts` (JWT + skip if public), `banned.guard.ts`, `roles.guard.ts`
- **Decorators:** `public.decorator.ts`, `roles.decorator.ts`, `current-user.decorator.ts`
- **JWT payload shape:** `src/auth/jwt-payload.type.ts`

## Data layer

- **Schema & enums (source of truth):** `prisma/schema.prisma`
- **Migrations:** `prisma/migrations/`
- **Seed (admin/user test accounts):** `prisma/seed.ts`
- **Prisma 7 config:** `prisma.config.ts`
- **DB client in app:** `src/prisma/prisma.service.ts`, `src/prisma/prisma.module.ts`

## API testing & docs

- Postman: `postman/Task-Board-API.postman_collection.json`
- Human-readable route list: `README.md`

When adding a feature, match the existing **module + controller + service + dto/** layout under `src/<feature>/`.
